title: Are You Actually Committed to Your Goals?
itunes:title: Are You Actually Committed to Your Goals?
description:
How committed are you to your goals? Are they "it would be nice to hit this goal" or "I am committed to hitting this goal, no matter what"? In this episode, I am going to teach you how to get committed to the goals you set for yourself. 

 

Follow me on IG for more inspiration here: https://www.instagram.com/robdialjr/
